"1  sheet (14 oz.) or 2 sheets (17.5 oz. total) frozen puff pastry, thawed according to package instructions","1 tablespoon beaten egg","5  medium rainbow carrots with tops (1 1/4 lbs., any colors except purple; if no tops, use flat-leaf parsley)","1/2 cup diced Spanish chorizo","1 tablespoon extra-virgin olive oil","1/2 teaspoon kosher salt","1/4 teaspoon pepper","3 ounces cream cheese, at room temperature","1/2 cup crumbled feta cheese, divided"